text: High Orchard Bridge High Orchard Bridge is a bridge over the Gloucester and Sharpness Canal in High Orchard in the city of Gloucester, England. It was opened in 2008 to carry the newly constructed St Ann Way over the canal.High Orchard Lift Bridge. Eadon Consulting. Retrieved 22 March 2019.High Orchard Bridge.
